I've used something similar in the past for non-array args:
Input {
    String? max_read_length 
}
…
String max_read_length_arg = if defined(max_read_length) then " --max_read_length " else ""
...
command {
...
~{max_read_length_arg}~{default="" sep=" --max_read_length " max_read_length} 
...
}

I just didn't know there was something nicer with newer WDL versions.

